{"id": "cross_001_zh", "question": "比较 DnD、BTD 和 NeuroDeX 三种 DNN 反编译器的核心方法。它们共同使用了什么技术？各自的策略有何不同？", "answer_type": "comparison", "should_answer": true, "gold_facts": ["DnD 使用循环分析和选择性符号执行，配合模板 AST 匹配。", "BTD 使用表示学习进行算子分类，动态分析恢复网络拓扑，基于轨迹的符号执行恢复维度和参数。", "NeuroDeX 使用多阶段方法，包括算子检测、结构恢复和语义推断。", "三者都旨在从编译后的二进制文件中恢复高层 DNN 表示，但在处理编译器多样性和 ISA 支持方面策略不同。"], "expected_sources": [{"filename_contains": "DnD", "pages_any": [2, 7]}, {"filename_contains": "Decompiling x86", "pages_any": [2, 5]}, {"filename_contains": "NeuroDeX", "pages_any": [2, 3]}], "must_contain": ["DnD", "BTD", "符号执行", "反编译"], "must_not_contain": ["无法找到"], "expected_chunk_ids": ["a35868aae0e5b52e", "a49cff7c87b55699", "419fc6373eaa3a11", "dd14fdbbc8aab685", "15b8cc328b261621", "c7cae06ab0913f65", "601eb5b0afc04577", "e6fa0a5eab9324b8", "0fe413d265df53df", "20ac523f29224b53", "16dc5ceb2dad79e0", "8bc39bce9bf2852f", "9bdf3eaa138e61a4", "1fba7167150e9c4c", "8d4c6565f46d91f8", "75400e9cae287630", "07bd4026dc6d2bf8", "de512af1fa4b48f3", "71e4a92ee18698c0", "8b2f1dfb72bfacf4", "3d64bffd19474970", "2eda3aacde4e38c8", "efb62b56cbcc5dea", "09693a185e42519d", "1abbd1f5f8db7fc2", "07d58c1a191e9499", "6647adfcb117af59", "2c7d44730d74e147", "dd6347b07eaca9c2"]}
