{"id": "cross_003_zh", "question": "比较 FlatD 和 MACO 保护 DNN 模型免受逆向工程攻击的防御策略。它们各自使用了哪些编译器技术？", "answer_type": "comparison", "should_answer": true, "gold_facts": ["FlatD 基于 O-LLVM 使用控制流平坦化，并将保护嵌入 TVM 代码生成流水线。", "MACO 使用编译器级别的混淆，包括混淆强度控制策略来防止模型提取。", "两者都在编译器层面操作，但 FlatD 专注于 CFG 混淆，而 MACO 引入了更广泛的混淆原语。"], "expected_sources": [{"filename_contains": "FlatD", "pages_any": [2, 4]}, {"filename_contains": "MACO", "pages_any": [2, 3]}], "must_contain": ["FlatD", "MACO", "混淆", "编译器"], "must_not_contain": ["无法找到"], "expected_chunk_ids": ["0b3fd223c77290d0", "9993bde5022b6c59", "347cb9d0884d62c1", "241543cef9ddd0b4", "2e79fb7bed8a4c7a", "f73b5f75aac3ec83", "2338dcc55b3e6bfb", "ad1a91cc542b6d8f", "f62fe1db42999591", "bf5a571d04f8b152", "c5a41f9539bbbbb3", "6d2b8a2fdd807fb8", "7e631bb1c1927f80", "5cd6db0d571f3d01", "b2c4f775f24f29aa", "a2d9dfe5fdaafa61", "cf394da77264083d", "00ccfa4fd9f4b9f3", "3cd959dc2fd2e469", "3a1ec23543fdf79f", "c2b5c53a428f560a", "2efa81925113e6fe", "2ac627b9f9362315", "c6ef9e4e6514fc1a", "b28b9ba52fd8481d", "4b74a8626492bbc5", "c64f0833a1870f74", "18d3f6e7feba0426"]}
{"id": "cross_004_zh", "question": "DnD、BTD 和 NeuroDeX 在 DNN 加速器支持和基于解释器的编译方面有哪些共同的局限性？", "answer_type": "comparison", "should_answer": true, "gold_facts": ["三种反编译器都不支持或难以处理针对专用加速器编译的 DNN 二进制文件。", "DnD 明确排除了基于解释器的编译方案和加速器二进制文件，原因是反汇编器限制。", "BTD 以 x86 为目标，其他架构需要重新适配工具链。", "NeuroDeX 跨多个平台但仍面临多样化加速器 ISA 的挑战。"], "expected_sources": [{"filename_contains": "DnD", "pages_any": [5]}, {"filename_contains": "Decompiling x86", "pages_any": [2]}, {"filename_contains": "NeuroDeX", "pages_any": [5, 6]}], "must_contain": ["加速器", "解释器", "ISA", "不支持"], "must_not_contain": ["支持所有硬件平台", "无法找到"], "expected_chunk_ids": ["c4cbc45c8570e30a", "4b4a4ad864c4b875", "49fe88a7eaee3e40", "a1922c6875e023e8", "ee023a9e8f2f057c", "17bd53439cd2266e", "0dc6e57707061f64", "7a03f3ec50760ad9", "da2e9320264c822e", "220c6ec918025b7a", "104eb05efbb3350f", "bedca5e784a8ba90", "e722f507cd314f56", "ab34bb9750cf1e98", "7a9e9e6eeae883c2", "894732320b6c03e7", "017ece968e194724", "e528851b2d3e6168", "95e5c6783e018daf", "e79085d67d3f03cb"]}
