{"id": "cross_006_zh", "question": "哪些论文讨论了控制流平坦化作为保护技术？它们的应用有何不同？", "answer_type": "comparison", "should_answer": true, "gold_facts": ["FlatD 基于 O-LLVM 使用控制流平坦化来保护 DNN 程序的控制流图。", "FlatD 专门针对 TVM 编译器的代码生成阶段。", "控制流平坦化在编译器保护中被讨论为混淆原语之一。"], "expected_sources": [{"filename_contains": "FlatD", "pages_any": [2, 4]}], "must_contain": ["控制流平坦化", "O-LLVM", "FlatD"], "must_not_contain": ["无法找到"], "expected_chunk_ids": ["0b3fd223c77290d0", "9993bde5022b6c59", "347cb9d0884d62c1", "241543cef9ddd0b4", "2e79fb7bed8a4c7a", "f73b5f75aac3ec83", "2338dcc55b3e6bfb", "ad1a91cc542b6d8f", "f62fe1db42999591", "bf5a571d04f8b152", "c5a41f9539bbbbb3", "6d2b8a2fdd807fb8", "7e631bb1c1927f80", "5cd6db0d571f3d01"]}
{"id": "cross_007_zh", "question": "TVM 和 Glow 等 DNN 编译器在 DNN 反编译和保护论文中扮演什么角色？哪些论文同时评估了这两个编译器？", "answer_type": "comparison", "should_answer": true, "gold_facts": ["TVM 和 Glow 是生产级 DNN 编译器，在反编译和保护研究中被用作编译目标。", "BTD 在 TVM、Glow 和 NNFusion 上进行了评估。", "DnD 在多种 ISA 上评估了 Glow 和 TVM。", "FlatD 将其保护嵌入到 TVM 代码生成流水线中。"], "expected_sources": [{"filename_contains": "DnD", "pages_any": [3]}, {"filename_contains": "Decompiling x86", "pages_any": [2]}, {"filename_contains": "FlatD", "pages_any": [2]}], "must_contain": ["TVM", "Glow", "编译器", "DNN"], "must_not_contain": ["无法找到"], "expected_chunk_ids": ["e6fa0a5eab9324b8", "ec71df9e40361439", "f3c8f2140ec6c9b2", "9ebc6fdc922a39af", "f951d7957c759b17", "8a1d08f4ae4a79b8", "fb203cac697bbb6b", "7776f566aa69629d", "0b3fd223c77290d0", "9993bde5022b6c59", "347cb9d0884d62c1", "241543cef9ddd0b4", "2e79fb7bed8a4c7a", "f73b5f75aac3ec83", "2338dcc55b3e6bfb", "ad1a91cc542b6d8f"]}
{"id": "cross_008_zh", "question": "符号执行在 DNN 反编译中起什么作用？总结 DnD、BTD 和 NeuroDeX 各自如何使用符号执行。", "answer_type": "comparison", "should_answer": true, "gold_facts": ["DnD 使用选择性符号执行生成算子摘要并捕获数学语义。", "BTD 使用基于轨迹的符号执行配合污点分析来恢复维度和参数。", "NeuroDeX 也使用符号分析技术来恢复算子语义。", "三者的符号执行都有助于恢复 DNN 算子执行的数学操作。"], "expected_sources": [{"filename_contains": "DnD", "pages_any": [7]}, {"filename_contains": "Decompiling x86", "pages_any": [5]}, {"filename_contains": "NeuroDeX", "pages_any": [3, 4]}], "must_contain": ["符号执行", "算子", "恢复"], "must_not_contain": ["无法找到"], "expected_chunk_ids": ["0fe413d265df53df", "20ac523f29224b53", "16dc5ceb2dad79e0", "8bc39bce9bf2852f", "9bdf3eaa138e61a4", "1fba7167150e9c4c", "8d4c6565f46d91f8", "efb62b56cbcc5dea", "09693a185e42519d", "1abbd1f5f8db7fc2", "07d58c1a191e9499", "6647adfcb117af59", "2c7d44730d74e147", "dd6347b07eaca9c2", "2f2cb9ddcb1914fa", "03e5ee11ed5284cb", "5ef98db39307ff3e", "62cf5a5130e8a5fd", "da2e9320264c822e"]}
